<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 05:58:10 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》推繁中版，中文官網站＋ YouTube 預告影片同步公開</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/19/pretty-derby-youtube/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=pretty-derby-youtube</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 05:58:10 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[cygames]]></category><category><![CDATA[小萌科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[賽馬娘 Pretty Derby]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086759</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>台灣小萌科技（Komoe Game）於周二（15 日）宣布，正式由日本遊戲企業 Cygames 取得《賽馬娘 P [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>台灣小萌科技（Komoe Game）於周二（15 日）宣布，正式由日本遊戲企業 Cygames 取得《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》的代理權，將會推出繁中版遊戲，並同步公開中文官方網站和 YouTube 預告影片。</p><p>《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》為 Cygames 的代表作之一，曾推出音樂、漫畫、電視動畫等範疇的周邊作品。另於 2021 年 2 月 24 日在日本發行首個手遊，遊戲的註冊人數於開服前已突破 60 萬，隨即蟬聯各大平台排行榜第一名，引起全國關注。</p><p>故事講述，長有馬耳與尾巴的「賽馬娘」繼承了日本實際存在的賽馬名稱與靈魂，需與夥伴及訓練員一起度過學園生活，亦敵亦友，努力稱霸「閃耀系列賽」為目標的故事。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-694x306.png" alt="" width="694" height="306" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-694x306.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-1280x565.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-768x339.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-1536x678.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02-2048x904.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.45.02.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58-2048x1013.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.47.58.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》是款模擬養成遊戲，玩家化身成「特雷森學園」的新人訓練員，為賽馬娘按排訓練並透過與她們相處，協力合作，努力朝目標競賽前進。而賽馬娘的競賽過程及演出會以 3D 模組呈現，於競賽結束後她們更會透過「勝利演唱會」載歌載舞感謝粉絲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26-2048x1013.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.46.26.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56-2048x1013.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-17-下午 7.48.56.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>日本版推出至今未曾跌出日本雙系統暢銷榜的 15 名外。據外媒報道，《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》2021 年的全年營利約 10 億美元（約 7.8 億港元），帶挈母公司 CyberAgent 的註冊帳戶於 5 個月內累計共 900 萬人次。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_97872"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I2N75EUQX_0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://uma.komoejoy.com">《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》官網</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
