</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>美國迪士尼將開發住宅區「迪士尼的故事生活」 隨時生活在迪士尼童話</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/19/disney-is-developing-planned-communities-for-fans-who-never-want-to-leave-its-clutches/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=disney-is-developing-planned-communities-for-fans-who-never-want-to-leave-its-clutches</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 05:54:37 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活娛樂]]></category><category><![CDATA[Disney]]></category><category><![CDATA[Storyliving by Disney]]></category><category><![CDATA[迪士尼]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086649</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>迪士尼日前宣佈，正計劃在美國各地開發住宅房地產項目，並將其命名為「迪士尼的故事生活」(Storyliving  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">迪士尼日前宣佈，正計劃在美國各地開發住宅房地產項目，並將其命名為「迪士尼的故事生活」(Storyliving by Disney)。首項目將在加州 Rancho Mirage 開始實行，正研究在美國其他地點推行。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09-1280x852.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09-768x511.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09-1536x1023.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D7E8514-4DDC-4BE5-973E-E2FDCF52DB09.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">華特迪士尼曾表示，他的終極夢想是希望打造一個「明日世界中的實驗性社區」般的理想住宅，而是次推出的「Storyliving by Disney」就是基於此作構思。迪士尼樂園、體驗和產品部總裁 Josh D’Amaro 表示，計畫將發揮迪士尼精神，用「故事」拓展至人們日常的食衣住行育樂等項目。被稱為「Cotino」的 Rancho Mirage 項目是迪士尼和專門從事規劃社區的 DMB 開發公司（DMB Development）合作建設，佔地 24 英畝，提供住宅樓、獨幢住宅和共管公寓讓買家選擇。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA-694x320.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="320" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA-694x320.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA-1280x591.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA-768x354.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA-1536x709.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/951A4F9C-4100-4BDD-A1DE-AED90A6A46CA.jpeg 1599w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0-694x360.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0-694x360.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0-1280x665.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0-768x399.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0-1536x798.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/645732B3-FC16-4189-987B-AC44CE8E1BA0.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Walt Disney Imagineering 的執行製片人 Michael Hundgen 表示，每個 Storyliving By Disney 社區將會有「獨特的室內和室外空間，為居民提供探索、參與和創造他們自身故事的機會，每個人都會活在自己的故事當中」。住宅社區面向所有年齡層，但所有社區亦將特別設立一個供 55 歲以上長者居住的區域。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49-694x435.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49-694x435.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49-1280x803.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49-768x482.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49-1536x964.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/F18FD31C-34BA-428D-B69A-347092BEFF49.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926-694x319.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926-694x319.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926-1280x588.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926-768x353.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926-1536x706.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/61C142A1-64C5-40ED-AA26-55BA32263926.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在社區營運方面，將有接受過迪士尼傳奇客服培訓的員工負責，迪士尼幻想工程師（Disney Imagineers）亦將幫助社區發展。社區居民可透過會員資格進入一些特殊的俱樂部，當中提供各式各樣的娛樂體驗、健康課程，以及研討會等。為了讓居民不會忘記身在迪士尼，需要時社區內將會有迪士尼人物出現為居民提供協助，恍惚長期住在迪士尼度假村。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_27298"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4CVucnt46ww?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/2/16/22937210/disney-residential-communities-storyliving-cotino-planned-town">THE VERGE</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
