</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple 邀南韓導演用 iPhone 13 Pro 拍古裝片，導演稱畫質效果可登銀幕</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/19/apple-shares-short-film-by-south-korean-director-park-chan-wook-shot-on-iphone-13-pro/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-shares-short-film-by-south-korean-director-park-chan-wook-shot-on-iphone-13-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 05:47:38 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[電影]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087047</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前在 YouTube 上分享了一部名為《Life is But a Dream》的微電影，該影片 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 早前在 YouTube 上分享了一部名為《Life is But a Dream》的微電影，該影片由韓國知名導演樸讚鬱執導。過程中只用到了 iPhone 13 Pro 進行拍攝，令人不禁驚嘆於 iPhone 強大的拍攝效果。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-694x385.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-694x385.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-1280x710.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-768x426.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-1536x852.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6-2048x1136.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E5E939AF-13BD-45DC-BDE7-859FD69B31C6.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據外媒報導，《Life is But a Dream》是全程使用 iPhone 13 Pro 拍攝（Shot on iPhone）的系列短片，由「樸氏兄弟」樸讚鬱和樸讚景創作，片長約 20 分鐘。故事講述一名義士（柳海真飾）為了尋找能夠埋葬恩人（金玉彬飾）的棺材而挖掘了一個廢棄的墳墓，從而喚醒了墳墓的主人劍客（樸正民飾）。樸讚鬱表示，這次也並非兄弟二人首次嘗試以 iPhone 進行拍攝。早於 2011 年，他們已曾使用 iPhone4 拍攝了短片《波瀾萬丈》，當時確保畫質使用了特技效果，這次就完全沒有必要。即使用大螢幕放映，畫質表現亦依舊不錯。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_23850"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HnzKqxtnWDY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">樸讚鬱以《老男孩》、《小姐》、《親切的金子》等影片而聞名。Apple 是次透過「Shot on iPhone」的廣告活動邀請到樸讚鬱拍攝影片，還將其作品分享在 Apple 官方的 YouTube 頻道。Apple 亦上載了《Life is But a Dream》的製作特輯，開放供大家觀賞。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_15048"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pGr9dnynQcE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2022/02/17/apple-shares-short-film-by-south-korean-director-park-chan-wook-shot-on-iphone-13-pro/">9TO5Mac</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
